Manage Kafka streams groups.

Usage:
  confluent kafka streams-group [command]

Available Commands:
  describe                                 Describe a Kafka streams group.
  list                                     List Kafka streams groups.
  member                                   Manage Kafka streams group members.
  member-assignment                        Manage Kafka streams group member assignments.
  member-target-assignment                 Manage Kafka streams group member target assignments.
  member-target-assignment-task-partitions Manage Kafka streams group member target task partitions.
  member-task-partitions                   Manage Kafka streams group member task partitions.
  subtopology                              Manage Kafka streams group subtopologies.

Global Flags:
  -h, --help            Show help for this command.
      --unsafe-trace    Equivalent to -vvvv, but also log HTTP requests and responses which might contain plaintext secrets.
  -v, --verbose count   Increase verbosity (-v for warn, -vv for info, -vvv for debug, -vvvv for trace).

Use "confluent kafka streams-group [command] --help" for more information about a command.
